<div id="Idea_3072"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3072-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3072">Global Warming - they push exotic fixes while ignoring the simple fix&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
